text: Mark Doubleday (born 10 August 1973 in Sydney) is an Australian baseball player. He represented Australia at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Australian expatriate baseball players in the United States Category:Baseball players at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Louisiana Tech Bulldogs baseball players Category:Olympic baseball players of Australia Category:Sportspeople from Sydney
